name: citations.tsv.gz
description: contains data citations in a gzipped tab-separated values format. Note that each row in the interactions.tsv/csv files also contain citations.

name: citations.csv.gz
description: contains data citations in a in a gzipped comma-separated values format. Note that each row in interactions.tsv/csv files also contain citations.

name: interactions.tsv.gz
description: contains species interactions tabulated as pair-wise interactions in a gzipped tab-separated values format.

name: interactions.csv.gz
description: contains species interactions tabulated as pair-wise interactions in a gzipped comma-separated values format.

name: refuted-interactions.tsv.gz
description: contains refuted species interactions tabulated as pair-wise interactions in a gzipped tab-separated values format.

name: refuted-interactions.csv.gz
description: contains refuted species interactions tabulated as pair-wise interactions in a gzipped comma-separated values format.

name: interactions.nq.gz
description: contains species interactions expressed in the resource description framework in a gzipped rdf/quads format.

name: taxonMap.tsv.gz
description: describes how names in existing datasets were mapped into existing naming schemes in a gzipped tab-separated values format.

name: taxonCache.tsv.gz
description: contains hierarchies and identifiers associated with names from naming schemes in a gzipped tab-separated values format.

name: dwca.zip
description: contains species interactions data as a zip file resembing a Darwin Core Archive using a custom, occurrence level, association extension.

name: dwca-by-study.zip
description: contains species interactions data as a zip file resembling a Darwin Core Archive aggregated by study using a custom, occurrence level, association extension.

name: neo4j-graphdb.zip
description: contains a neo4j v3.5.29 database containing a graph representation of the species interaction data.
